    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, ProxyCreator
    public class Sensor
extends ComponentSensor
implements java.io.Serializable
    Sensor extends ComponentSensor, it is a leaf of the composite pattern. It is here to generate temperature values according to an algorithm passed through a Strategy pattern
